text.div: • Include codes from http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/v3-ObservationValue where concept is-a ELSTAT

name: ObservationEligibilityIndicatorValue
title: ObservationEligibilityIndicatorValue
description: Code specifying eligibility indicators used to assess or establish eligibility for coverage under a policy or program eligibility status, e.g., certificates of creditable coverage; student enrollment; adoption, marriage or birth certificate.
